  "detailed_description": "A convenient tool for game design, which can convert 2D plate into normal map of picture, and display tool of WYSIWYG<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn the game and image design, it is a tool for generating relative normal texture from pictures. Normal map can be used for bump texture, etc., which is convenient for the related functions of model subtraction<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe tool uses the physical material effect. If you want to achieve relevant functions, please refer to the physical material effect",
  "about_the_game": "A convenient tool for game design, which can convert 2D plate into normal map of picture, and display tool of WYSIWYG<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn the game and image design, it is a tool for generating relative normal texture from pictures. Normal map can be used for bump texture, etc., which is convenient for the related functions of model subtraction<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe tool uses the physical material effect. If you want to achieve relevant functions, please refer to the physical material effect",
